{"type":"HOSTEL","name":"Noah's Ark Flashpacker","nameEN":"Noah's Ark Flashpacker","isActive":true,"isNew":true,"description":"WELCOME TO NOAH’S ARK - Greymouth’s First Flashpacker in a Charming Heritage Setting. \r\n\r\nStep inside to discover a beautifully preserved interior, rich in original features and timeless charm. Every room tells a story, and every hallway echoes with history. Noah's Ark Flashpacker offers more than just a place to stay for travellers exploring the stunning West Coast — it’s an experience. A welcoming haven where heritage, hospitality, and heart come together. Whether you're here for adventure or relaxation, you'll enjoy this cosy accommodation, friendly atmosphere, and convenient access to local attractions. It is just a short walk from the town centre, with its cafés, bars, restaurants, galleries, supermarket, the TranzAlpine Railway Station and the Bus Station.\r\n\r\nYou can relax in the garden in hummocks, have a BBQ, unwind on the balcony while taking in breathtaking West Coast sunsets, or enjoy the renovated dining room and lounge. The fully equipped kitchen features top-range appliances, with complimentary tea, coffee, sugar, and salt provided for added convenience. Complimentary bikes are available for exploring the area and trying out the new coastal cycle-way. Helpful tips are provided for local bush walks, nearby beaches, and a variety of adventure activities. With unlimited free Wi-Fi it's easy to stay in touch with family and friends or plan your trip ahead. There is a log fire and a heat pump that keep things warm on cooler days. Also, book swap and lots of games. There is a separate TV room with new Samsung Smart TV and comfy sofas.\r\n\r\nEnjoy modern comforts, thoughtful design, and the warm hospitality that makes every stay memorable. \r\n\r\nStay. Feel. Experience.","hostelworldSays":null,"hostelSays":null,"businessNumber":"9429045538421","location":{"address1":"16 Chapel Street","address2":"Greymouth","city":{"id":336